# DevBarberShop WordPress Website

## Project Overview
DevBarberShop is a professional WordPress website for a barbershop, designed to provide an elegant and functional online presence for hair and grooming services.

## Features
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Online booking system
- Service showcase
- Team member profiles
- Gallery of haircuts and styles
- Contact information and location details

## Prerequisites
- WordPress 5.7+
- PHP 7.4 or higher
- MySQL 5.7 or MariaDB 10.3+

## Installation

### Manual Installation
1. Download the latest release
2. Upload to your WordPress `wp-content/themes` directory
3. Activate the theme in WordPress admin panel

### Recommended Plugins
- Contact Form 7
- Elementor Page Builder
- Yoast SEO
- WooCommerce (optional, for additional services)

## Customization
- Customize colors, logos, and branding in theme settings
- Add/edit services through WordPress admin
- Configure booking system preferences

